<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Category1 on Lucas`s blog</title><link>https://lucasss1916.github.io/categories/category1/</link><description>Recent content in Category1 on Lucas`s blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 16:47:24 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://lucasss1916.github.io/categories/category1/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Surge</title><link>https://lucasss1916.github.io/posts/surge-mac-%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0mihomo%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Oct 2025 16:47:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://lucasss1916.github.io/posts/surge-mac-%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0mihomo%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="下载mihomo核心-存入对应文件夹"&gt;下载mihomo核心 存入对应文件夹&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;下载相应的mihomo核心放入/usr/local/bin，并改名为mihomo，启动surge mac，如果是surge不支持的协议，自动调用mihomo，很方便，很贴心&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>部署blog</title><link>https://lucasss1916.github.io/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E5%92%8Cgithub%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BAblog/</link><pubDate>Sun, 31 Aug 2025 17:04:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://lucasss1916.github.io/posts/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E5%92%8Cgithub%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BAblog/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="1下载安装hugo"&gt;1.下载安装hugo&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1.在macos上安装hugo &lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;brew install hugo&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2.查看是否安装完成&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;hugo version&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3.如果正确输出.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;比如v0.133.1+extended darwin/amd64&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
则表示安装成功.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="2创建blog"&gt;2.创建blog&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;hugo new site hugo-blog&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;cd hugo-blog&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
创建主题.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;git init&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;git submoudle add https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-PaperMod.git themes/PaperMod&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
修改配置hugo.toml&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;baseURL = &amp;quot;https://yourname.github.io/&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;languageCode = &amp;quot;en-us&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;title = &amp;quot;My Hugo Blog&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;theme = &amp;quot;PaperMod&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
新建一篇文章&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;hugo new posts/hello-world.md&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br&gt;
本地预览,可通过1313端口访问&lt;br&gt;
&lt;code&gt;hugo server -D&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>